description:
HI2U

The Walking Dead: 400 Days DLC (c) Telltale Games

Release date : 9th of July, 2013
Protection   : Steam
Type         : Adventure
Size         : 45 x 100 mb

Notes

This DLC/addon release is complete and standalone

Description

Centered on a truck stop on a Georgia highway, this DLC episode for Season 1
of The Walking Dead by Telltale Games tells five linked stories of survival
in the wake of the zombie apocalypse. From day 1 of the undead plague to
400 days later, The Walking Dead: 400 Days offers more of the horror and
human drama of Robert Kirkman and Telltales award-winning series. Echoes
of the choices you made in Season 1 will carry over into '400 Days' and the
choices you make in '400 Days' will resonate into Season 2.

Install

Extract & mount the iso and install
Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack directory on the image
to your game install directory
Play the game
